title: PyCon Lithuania 2023
description:
PyCon Lithuania is the biggest Python and PyData gathering in Baltics and Nordics.

On May 18-19 it will feature talks by Travis Oliphant (numpy, NumFocus), Samuel Colvin (pydantic), Thomas Wiecki (PyMC), Ritchie Vink (polars) and 40+ other speakers
